508
00:24:04,900 --> 00:24:05,700
Yes.

509
00:24:07,340 --> 00:24:09,860
This is my home tutor.

510
00:24:11,700 --> 00:24:12,660
Sir.

511
00:24:12,660 --> 00:24:13,900
I'm really sorry.

512
00:24:13,900 --> 00:24:15,220
I forgot

513
00:24:15,220 --> 00:24:17,380
