523
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:42,330
Mom.

524
00:24:42,860 --> 00:24:43,810
I'm sorry.

525
00:24:43,810 --> 00:24:44,620
I'm late.

526
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:45,580
You're here.

527
00:24:45,580 --> 00:24:46,940
Our family

528
