529
00:24:48,620 --> 00:24:51,140
Nothing can be done without rules.

530
00:24:51,140 --> 00:24:51,780
Right.

531
00:24:51,780 --> 00:24:52,780
Mom, you're right.

532
00:24:52,780 --> 00:24:54,260
There was a traffic jam.

533
00:24:54,260 --> 00:24:55,340
