588
00:27:00,260 --> 00:27:01,060
No.

589
00:27:01,940 --> 00:27:04,340
You'll become a great mother.

590
00:27:04,340 --> 00:27:05,660
And now,

591
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:07,540
